@node BUGS

  - If you try to put in more then 20 characters in the password gadget it
    will not allow you to delete (Not my fault!!)

  - The keysupport for the password gadget is case sensitive it only
    works with lower-case letters!

  - Not really a bug or problem just untidy. The password gadget is not
    properly aligned (My fault!!) and I am trying to sort it.

@endnode
